#!/usr/bin/env python3
"""
pluck — Config Key-Path Tool  v1.1.0
Copy, merge, read, set, and diff values at dot-separated paths across
YAML, JSON, TOML, and .env files — one CLI, format-agnostic operations.

Architecture:
    format adapter (load → dict tree, write back with format fidelity)
        → dot-path navigation (nested dicts, list indices)
        → copy | merge | get | set | diff
        → optional backup / dry-run / cross-format transfer

Usage:
    pluck copy  SOURCE DEST model,providers,fallback_providers
    pluck merge SOURCE DEST providers
    pluck get   FILE model
    pluck set   FILE model gpt-4o
    pluck diff  A B model providers
    pluck doctor

Dependencies:
    pip install ruamel.yaml rich tomli-w
"""

